I would also say that I have nothing against NON RPers who do not get in the way.<br>
<br>
Someone wanders around on there own having fun, speaking to no one, well this does not detract from my enjoyment at all. Infact I have known many nice shy druids who like to do this. They do not RP but they do not get in ya face either.<br>
<br>
Lets face it, the NPCs in this game do not RP :-) in fact this lack of NPC RP is one of the things that detracts from the RP feel of the world BUT thats a different topic.<br>
